────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ISOLATED INSTANCES & MASTER KEY
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Each self-hosted node generates its own SOUL_MASTER_KEY and
operates as a fully isolated instance. Soul certificates issued
by one node are not valid on any other node. There is no central
authority or shared network — every node is sovereign.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ON-CHAIN ANCHORING (SMART CONTRACT)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
The SYS anchoring smart contract deployed at:
    0xB68Ca7cFFbe1113F62B3d0397d293693A8e0106B (Polygon Mainnet)

was deployed by Jan-Oliver Karo and collects a protocol fee
(anchorFee) for each soul anchor. The contract runs autonomously
on the Polygon blockchain. The deployer is not an intermediary —
on-chain transactions are irreversible and solely the
responsibility of the initiating user.

